name: BagofLaughs
0:
”Alexa, open Bag of Laughs.”
”Alexa, ask Bag of Laughs to tell me a joke.”
”Alexa, ask Bag of Laughs to say something funny.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: bag of laughs
des:
Increase your joke knowledge with Bag of Laughs!
Including jokes like:

• Why don't fish play basketball? Because they're afraid of the net.

• Helvetia, Arial and Times New Roman walk into a bar. Barman says, "We don't want your type in here."

• Doctor Doctor, I feel like a snooker ball. Get on the end of the cue.

...and many more!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
